paper_title: Finite-dimensional nilpotent Lie superalgebras of class two and skew-supersymmetric bilinear maps
abstract: In this article, we discuss the category $\mathcal{SN}_2$ where the objects are finite-dimensional nilpotent Lie superalgebras of class two and the category $\mathcal{SSKE}$ where the objects are skew-supersymmetric bilinear maps. We establish relation between $\mathcal{SN}_2$ and $\mathcal{SSKE}$. As a result, we discuss the capability of nilpotent Lie superalgebras of class two.
